{"tid":1861693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【無國界畜牲】紅十字會：捐來口罩許多「不合格」 竟撐武漢紅會不分發","createTime":"2020-02-04T08:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T09:27:39.000Z","uid":88167,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6367b02ee217567e012fa8a3ba42dfc27ff6e073","tid":1861693,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"武漢紅十字會連日被外界怒轟公眾捐贈的物資「不到位」，抗疫醫院收不到。紅十字會周一解釋，必須確保所有用於中國醫院的口罩都是高質素，指公眾若捐贈劣質口罩隨時「幫倒忙」。<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會與紅新月會國際聯合會（IFRC）新任總幹事恰帕蓋恩（Jagan Chapagain）承認，醫療物資供應的緊張。對於武漢紅十會被批評未能將中國各地捐贈的口罩送到前線醫院，他說：「武漢紅會近來未處理過類似情況，要在短時間內擴大行動，難免會有不足之處。」<br />\n恰帕蓋恩支持武漢紅會「刻意」決定扣起一些公眾捐贈的口罩，指那些口罩不宜給前線抗疫醫護人員，認為前線醫護人員必須用高質素口罩，要達到N95口罩標準，但許多捐來的口罩「不合格」。他呼籲捐贈者確保所有醫療裝備達一定質素，以免大量「劣質」口罩「阻住貨倉」。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情當頭，物資緊張，武漢紅會倉庫日前卻被卻發現堆滿物資，外界捐予抗疫最前線之協和醫院的3,000個口罩被「堵截」，遲遲未到位，又被踢爆有政府官員擅自於武漢紅會倉庫自行取走一箱口罩，司機被追問時竟稱「是領導需要」<br />\n<br />\nSource from <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200204/UP4QYIVFCJ5SXTPZCLLRCV4HL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200204%2FUP4QYIVFCJ5SXTPZCLLRCV4HL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=5b87a4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200204%2FUP4QYIVFCJ5SXTPZCLLRCV4HL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=b09c83f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200204/UP4QYIVFCJ5SXTPZCLLRCV4HL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n果然只有仆街先係無分國界<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a241aeced8a7bdcb964798c0411d3ad8cbbffd2","tid":1861693,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c6cf21567afd2ee162d23b49af860edf36f177b","tid":1861693,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ee7cd796c81e1e7484c15afc421eb9d812a146","tid":1861693,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"推上熱門：美孚人，今晚7點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1861651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1861651</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80628760e964532205b031dc052c3b358611c0ca","tid":1861693,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da32987e7dc764cd52d1643327d95e401380fc4b","tid":1861693,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRaN3Tq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRaN3Tq.jpg&h=7e5a2064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧小平弟弟，鄧墾，湖北原副省長「106歲已逝世」。<br />\n鄧坤娥，湖北省紅十字基金會理事長，湖北備災救災中心副主任科員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1nde0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1nde0g.jpg&h=cd394fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0XQhdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0XQhdP.jpg&h=005fcaa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1DTe0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1DTe0w.jpg&h=bc596707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPuyZsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPuyZsp.jpg&h=117ef025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"h